    Contact

    ContactList
    Saves a list of contacts to be used in conjunction with Events and Timers.
    ContactListsActivity.ContactListsAdapter
    Defines how the ContactLists are presented in the ListView.
    ContactsAdapter
    Specifies how a Contact will be shown as an item of a ListView.
    CreateEventActivity.TimerAdapter
    Specifies how the added Timers and ContactLists are presented during the creation of an Event.
    Event

    EventsActivity.EventsAdapter

    Accesses the GPS and provides the required functions to use it.
    Timer
    Used as attribute to Events.
